Name: Victorian Mysteries: The Yellow Room
About the game: In the hidden object adventure 'Victorian Mysteries: The Yellow Room' a young woman is attacked and murdered in the middle of the night inside a locked room. There are only two ways out: a dead- bolted door and a single window blocked by iron bars. How did the murderer escape? Solve this perplexing conundrum and thrilling riddle...
